   "desc": "<p></p><h3></h3><div data-youtube-video=\"\"><iframe start=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/CnE0Gugn98E?modestbranding=1&amp;rel=1\" rel=\"1\" modestbranding=\"true\" loop=\"false\" autoplay=\"false\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div><p></p><p><strong>Heroic Skill Core Prio for single target</strong></p><p>- Cordy &gt; Morokai &gt; Adentus</p><p><br><strong>PVE Rotation GS/Dag</strong></p><p>Pre Buffs - Poison</p><p></p><p>Opener -</p><p>Gia &gt; Willbreak &gt; Dash x2 &gt; Valiant Brawl &gt; Stun &gt; Guillo &gt; Fatal Stigma &gt; Umbral &gt; Frenzied Sword Dance &gt; Valiant Brawl &gt; Deathblow &gt; Thundercloud &gt; Reuse Poison</p><p><br>Mid Fight Combos/Flow -<br>Gia &gt; Willbreak &gt; Dash x2 &gt; Valiant Brawl &gt; Stun &gt; Guillo<br>Umbral &gt; Fatal Stigma &gt; Frenzied Sword Dance &gt; Valiant Brawl &gt; Deathblow &gt; Thundercloud</p><p></p><p>Fill valiant brawl before large skill hits when off cd for 2 second damage boost</p><p>Use Death Blow on CD (especially with Cordy GS as this will be you highest damage skill)</p><p>You can spread out your dash charges to extend the heavy attack buff</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>",
